<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://www.scp-wiki.net/local--files/calibri-s-mega-cool-art-page-it-s-mostly-just-icons-but-what/Memetic%20Agent%201" alt="Memetic%20Agent%201" class="image" /></div>
<p>Dear Mr. Bold,</p>
<p>You have been brought to our attention due to your outstanding academic record and your various personal achievements.</p>
<p>Recommendations by <a href="/scp-5018">your brother</a>, a current employee of our organization, were also helpful in making a decision. Mr. David Bold has already informed you of the sensitive nature of our organization, which is the reason we cannot provide you further information regarding us. We apologize for the inconvenience.</p>
<p>If you are interested, please reply to this message and we can schedule an interview. We will look forward to meeting you and working with you, <a href="/mission-decommission">Mr. Bold</a>.</p>
<p>If you are not interested, please delete this message. Sharing this message is impossible, but attempting to do so will result in severe repercussions.</p>
<p>Sincerely, the SCP Foundation.</p>
